---
import MySiteLayout from "../layouts/layout.astro";
---

<MySiteLayout title="Gruppe 6">

<section class="text-center p-6">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Welcome to Gruppe 6</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">We are a team of talented individuals dedicated to disrupting the skies and silencing the drones.</p>
  <p class="mb-6">With our expertise in code conjuring, algorithm alchemy, power sage wisdom, and circuitry craftsmanship, we are on a mission to create innovative solutions that ground the drones and ensure a safer future.</p>
  <p class="mb-6">Get to know our team of professionals who are passionate about pushing the boundaries of technology and making a difference.</p>
</section>

  
  <section class="text-center p-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Meet Our Team</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Get to know the professionals.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-10 justify-items-center align-items-center">
      <div class="max-w-sm bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
        <img src="/Stian.jpg" alt="Stian" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-3">Stian</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          The Code Conjurer - With a keyboard as his wand and a mind brimming with spells of logic, Stian weaves enchantments into software, crafting the digital keys to disrupt the skies and ground the drones.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-sm bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
        <img src="/Anders.jpg" alt="Anders" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-3">Anders</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          The Algorithm Alchemist - In the labyrinth of code, Anders mixes potions of algorithms, transforming base data into golden insights that navigate our quest to silence the drones' whispering wings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-sm bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
        <img src="/Helge.jpg" alt="Helge" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-3">Helge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          The Power Sage - Drawing from the ancient wells of electrons, Helge ensures our devices thrive not just on power but on wisdom. Under his guidance, our gadgets sip energy, ready to stand the test of time and drones.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-sm bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4">
        <img
          src="/Andreas.jpg"
          alt="Andreas"
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-3">Andreas</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          The Circuitry Craftsman - Amidst a forest of wires and the scent of soldering, Andreas sculpts the heart of our project. His creations buzz with the power to mute the skies, grounding drones with an electric whisper.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MySiteLayout>
